    "rich_text_fM9R3M": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_NCrTWU": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>1. Introduction</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "text_color": "heading"
          }
        },
        "text_JKrXVN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This Privacy Policy describes how Madshades Technologies Pvt. Ltd. (“The EleFant,” “we,” “us,” or “our”) collects, uses, discloses, and protects your personal information when you use our website toys.theelefant.ai, mobile application, or any related services (collectively, the “Service”).</p><p>By accessing or using the Service, you consent to the collection and use of your information in accordance with this Policy. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.</p><p>This Policy is issued in compliance with the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023, the Information Technology Act, 2000, and related rules framed thereunder.</p>",
            "text_color": "main",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "heading_438LWc": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>2. Information We Collect</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "text_color": "heading"
          }
        },
        "text_3Ma4jp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>2.1 Information you provide directly</strong></p><p>• <strong>Account information:</strong> name, email address, mobile number, password, and profile details.</p><p>• <strong>Child-related details:</strong> child's first name, age or date of birth, and developmental stage (provided voluntarily to help us recommend age-appropriate toys).</p><p>• <strong>Transaction information:</strong> delivery address, billing address, and purchase history for toys bought, sold back, or exchanged.</p><p>• <strong>Payment information:</strong> processed securely through our payment gateway partners; we do not store full card numbers or CVVs on our servers.</p><p>• <strong>Communications:</strong> feedback, reviews, support queries, and any other information you share with us.</p><p><strong>2.2 Information collected automatically</strong></p><p>• <strong>Device and log data:</strong> IP address, device type, operating system, browser type, app version, and crash logs.</p><p>• <strong>Usage data:</strong> pages visited, features used, time spent, search queries, clicks, and referral sources.</p><p>• <strong>Location data:</strong> approximate location derived from IP address or pincode to determine serviceability and delivery logistics.</p><p>• <strong>Cookies and similar technologies:</strong> see Section 5 for details.</p>",
            "text_color": "main",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "heading_W99tk8": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>3. How We Use Your Information</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h2",
            "text_color": "heading"
          }
        },
        "text_Nz4PjH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p><p>• To create and manage your account, process orders, arrange deliveries, and handle sell-back pickups.</p><p>• To calculate and disburse sell-back payouts, process refunds, and maintain transaction records.</p><p>• To verify identity, prevent fraud, and enforce our Terms of Service.</p><p>• To personalise toy recommendations based on your child's age and interests.</p><p>• To send order updates, service-related communications, and (with your consent) promotional offers.</p><p>• To provide customer support and respond to your queries.</p><p>• To improve the Service, conduct analytics, and develop new features.</p><p>• To comply with legal obligations, tax requirements, and enforceable government requests.</p>",
            "text_color": "main",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
